00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:38.880 line:80%
How did you end up in such a sorry state?

00:00:43.240 --> 00:00:44.320 line:80%
Fate toys with us all.

00:00:45.320 --> 00:00:46.600 line:80%
Who could have foreseen this?

00:00:49.040 --> 00:00:50.240 line:80%
But duty bound me.

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:52.720 line:80%
I did all that I could.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:56.440 line:80%
As Military Administrator,

00:00:58.200 --> 00:00:59.800 line:80%
you were charged with overseeing the army.

00:01:00.400 --> 00:01:02.360 line:80%
Yet the rebel Sui Yuanhuai

00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:03.840 line:80%
has slipped away time and again.

00:01:04.480 --> 00:01:05.640 line:80%
You cannot evade responsibility.

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:09.200 line:80%
This was indeed my failure in duty.

00:01:10.040 --> 00:01:12.920 line:80%
I have already reported it
in a memorial to His Majesty

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:15.040 line:80%
and asked to be punished.

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:26.360 line:80%
You served under General He for years.

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:29.400 line:80%
You must know Li Bai's poem
<i>South of the City Walls</i>.

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:33.080 line:80%
<i>The soldiers lie scattered in the weeds</i>
<i>While the generals bear empty titles</i>

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:35.480 line:80%
For the sake of so-called legitimacy,

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:38.520 line:80%
countless lives have been sacrificed.

00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:39.480 line:80%
What cruelty.

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:41.640 line:80%
You call it a failure in duty.

00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:44.440 line:80%
Do you know how many soldiers' sacrifices
have come to nothing?

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:46.280 line:80%
How many civilians are trapped in misery?

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:49.280 line:80%
I carry the shame deeply.

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:55.360 line:80%
As the eldest grandson of the Lis,

00:01:56.720 --> 00:01:57.880 line:80%
I alone shall bear

00:01:59.080 --> 00:02:00.680 line:80%
the infamy for generations.

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:05.960 line:80%
A senseless fabricated war.

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:09.040 line:80%
Fallen soldiers into restless ghosts.

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:10.439 line:80%
Can you shoulder that weight?

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:13.640 line:80%
Lord Li,

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:16.480 line:80%
let me remind you of something.

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.560 line:80%
Do not forget why you entered
official service.

00:02:36.760 --> 00:02:38.440 line:80%
What did Marquis Wu'an say?

00:02:38.520 --> 00:02:39.800 line:80%
Xie Zheng…

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:44.840 line:80%
He likely knows everything now.

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:17.720 line:20%
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL <i>ZHU YU</i>
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

00:04:20.520 --> 00:04:23.360 line:20%
SESAME FLATBREAD

00:04:26.760 --> 00:04:29.520 line:80%
What sins did the Liu family commit
to suffer this?

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:31.720 line:80%
Their whole household was slaughtered.

00:04:31.800 --> 00:04:32.640 line:80%
WANTED, PUBLIC NOTICE

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:34.160 line:80%
The bandits are ruthless.

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:36.520 line:80%
What is one Liu household?

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:38.640 line:80%
The entire town of Lin'an was wiped out.

00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:42.320 line:80%
No wonder Marquis Wu'an
went after Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:04:43.280 --> 00:04:45.320 line:80%
He is truly ridding the people of evil.

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:46.320 line:80%
That is right.

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:48.920 line:80%
Look at this young woman.
Pretty as a flower.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:52.040 line:80%
Yet she calls herself a bandit?
Leader of Qingfeng Stronghold?

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:54.000 line:80%
-Five stuffed flatbreads.
-All right.

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:55.840 line:80%
-Bah.
-Here you go.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:05.920 line:80%
Watch out where you are going.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:39.080 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing…

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:44.880 line:80%
You heartless bastard.

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:47.400 line:80%
Where the hell did you disappear to?

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:52.640 line:80%
The authorities are hunting me.

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:55.560 line:80%
The outlaws are hunting me.

00:05:56.600 --> 00:06:00.000 line:80%
Even the deaths of 13 in the Liu household
have been pinned on me.

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:02.680 line:80%
Now I am being chased

00:06:03.200 --> 00:06:05.440 line:80%
like a stray dog.

00:06:05.520 --> 00:06:06.520 line:80%
And you…

00:06:07.320 --> 00:06:08.800 line:80%
Not even a trace of you.

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:37.680 line:80%
<i>Is that not the official from Lin'an?</i>

00:06:37.760 --> 00:06:39.040 line:80%
<i>What is he doing here?</i>

00:07:12.080 --> 00:07:15.000 line:80%
SOVEREIGN AND EFFICACIOUS

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:23.760 line:80%
Have some hot tea
to ward off the cold, Your Highness.

00:07:27.960 --> 00:07:29.880 line:80%
We are not far from the capital now.

00:07:30.400 --> 00:07:32.760 line:80%
Once we arrive there, you will be safe.

00:07:35.600 --> 00:07:36.720 line:80%
Qi Min!

00:07:37.320 --> 00:07:38.920 line:80%
Get out here!

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:47.480 line:80%
<i>Again?</i>

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:51.240 line:80%
His nose is sharper than a hunting dog.
He truly is impossible to shake.

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:35.080 line:80%
I will kill you, you wretched bastard,

00:08:35.680 --> 00:08:37.800 line:80%
then go join Father
and Mother in the afterlife.

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:42.479 line:80%
You stole my brother's name
and lived under it for over a decade.

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:46.720 line:80%
Surely you have nothing left to say.

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:49.480 line:80%
Yuanqing.

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:53.480 line:80%
Do not call me that.

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:05.600 line:80%
Yuanqing.

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:07.480 line:80%
If you resent me,

00:09:08.840 --> 00:09:10.440 line:80%
then please accept my apology.

00:09:10.520 --> 00:09:12.360 line:80%
Believe it or not,

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:15.120 line:80%
I never meant to harm you.

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:20.560 line:80%
Never meant to harm me?

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:22.200 line:80%
Then what about my mother?

00:09:22.840 --> 00:09:24.560 line:80%
What wrong did she ever do to you?

00:09:24.640 --> 00:09:27.680 line:80%
Answer me. Answer me!

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:52.320 line:80%
Is this what you mean…

00:09:54.440 --> 00:09:56.280 line:80%
by never meaning to harm me?

00:09:58.640 --> 00:09:59.560 line:80%
Yuanqing.

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:01.880 line:80%
I warned you long ago

00:10:02.680 --> 00:10:04.400 line:80%
not to be so arrogant.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:07.520 line:80%
Now I will finish the saying for you.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:12.240 line:80%
Those who act so meet a violent end.

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:29.960 line:80%
I was a fool.

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:32.480 line:80%
I always treated you as my own brother.

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:35.360 line:80%
I could not even bring myself to kill you.

00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:43.280 line:80%
Your family owes me a debt!

00:10:43.800 --> 00:10:46.320 line:80%
The entire household of Prince Changxin
deserves to die!

00:10:49.520 --> 00:10:51.320 line:80%
Why is it you grew strong and capable,

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:53.760 line:80%
while I became this half man, half ghost?

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:55.600 line:80%
Why could you train in martial arts,

00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:57.400 line:80%
ride horses, shoot arrows,

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:00.680 line:80%
while I was left with sickness,
forced to swallow medicine day after day?

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:05.560 line:80%
The pain in my heart
and the wounds on my body

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:08.640 line:80%
were all caused by Prince Changxin
and Wei Yan.

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:11.320 line:80%
My father. My mother.

00:11:11.840 --> 00:11:14.320 line:80%
I must avenge them.

00:11:14.400 --> 00:11:18.040 line:80%
Every one of you
will meet a miserable end!

00:11:21.880 --> 00:11:24.240 line:80%
You speak as if you are righteous.

00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:28.600 line:80%
Yet my mother never treated you poorly.

00:11:29.520 --> 00:11:31.680 line:80%
It was the Crown Princess
who killed my brother.

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:35.160 line:80%
My mother raised you
for more than ten years.

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:37.600 line:80%
You stole my brother's place.

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:41.320 line:80%
How could you bring yourself to kill her?

00:11:44.760 --> 00:11:47.080 line:80%
Because my heart died long ago.

00:11:48.280 --> 00:11:50.880 line:80%
Of course I could do it.

00:11:55.760 --> 00:11:57.800 line:80%
We must go, Your Highness.
This place is not safe.

00:12:31.520 --> 00:12:32.600 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing,

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:35.080 line:80%
have you forgotten

00:12:35.840 --> 00:12:37.800 line:80%
what I once taught you?

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.680 line:80%
Those who show mercy

00:12:42.400 --> 00:12:45.440 line:80%
have no place in a land of killing.

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:47.680 line:80%
And do not even dream

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:51.000 line:80%
of ruling this world.

00:14:12.120 --> 00:14:13.800 line:80%
Your Highness.
I came as quickly as I could.

00:14:16.520 --> 00:14:18.360 line:80%
Why not come after I'm dead instead?

00:14:20.640 --> 00:14:22.520 line:80%
It was your Li clan who sent word to me,

00:14:22.600 --> 00:14:24.240 line:80%
saying everything had been arranged.

00:14:24.320 --> 00:14:26.800 line:80%
Yet what awaited me along the way?

00:14:27.480 --> 00:14:29.720 line:80%
Xie Zheng's personal guards

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:32.320 line:80%
and that madman Sui Yuanqing.

00:14:34.200 --> 00:14:35.840 line:80%
This was indeed my failing.

00:14:36.720 --> 00:14:37.960 line:80%
Punish me as you see fit.

00:14:40.360 --> 00:14:41.680 line:80%
I know you do not like me.

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:44.320 line:80%
Protecting me, saving me…

00:14:44.840 --> 00:14:46.880 line:80%
You only do it
because your grandfather commands it.

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:49.600 line:80%
But now that you have boarded this ship,

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:51.680 line:80%
there is no turning back.

00:14:53.080 --> 00:14:55.080 line:80%
Only by seeing me safely into the capital

00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:58.000 line:80%
will your Li clan
have even the slightest chance.

00:14:58.520 --> 00:15:00.240 line:80%
All those years of planning
won't be wasted.

00:15:03.040 --> 00:15:05.920 line:80%
Otherwise,
I will drag us all down together.

00:15:06.680 --> 00:15:09.120 line:80%
Your Li clan will be wiped out,

00:15:09.200 --> 00:15:11.960 line:80%
and Wei Yan will sit in power
for decades to come.

00:15:12.760 --> 00:15:14.280 line:80%
The people will suffer endlessly.

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:22.080 line:80%
I have heard you care deeply
for common folks.

00:15:23.200 --> 00:15:25.240 line:80%
Surely you don't wish
for war and bloodshed to rise again.

00:15:28.880 --> 00:15:29.760 line:80%
I will

00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:32.400 line:80%
do everything in my power.

00:15:34.440 --> 00:15:35.280 line:80%
One more thing.

00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:38.040 line:80%
I do not care how you do it.

00:15:39.040 --> 00:15:40.960 line:80%
Kill Yu Bao'er,

00:15:41.040 --> 00:15:43.120 line:80%
and bring Yu Qianqian to me
without a single scratch.

00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:45.480 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:15:46.800 --> 00:15:49.200 line:80%
I heard Yu Bao'er is your only bloodline.

00:15:50.080 --> 00:15:51.000 line:80%
I do not acknowledge him.

00:15:51.520 --> 00:15:53.120 line:80%
That bloodline would only be my ruin.

00:15:54.920 --> 00:15:55.960 line:80%
One worthless life

00:15:56.600 --> 00:15:58.160 line:80%
against the fate of the Li clan.

00:15:58.240 --> 00:16:01.040 line:80%
You know well enough which matters more.

00:16:18.600 --> 00:16:20.480 line:80%
SOVEREIGN AND EFFICACIOUS

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:24.840 line:80%
If you fail to find the person I want,

00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:27.120 line:80%
then the alliance between me and the Lis

00:16:27.640 --> 00:16:28.920 line:80%
ends here.

00:16:38.280 --> 00:16:40.600 line:80%
He repaid kindness with blood.
Brother against brother.

00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:42.680 line:80%
Now he hunts his own son.

00:16:44.080 --> 00:16:45.680 line:80%
How can a man with no loyalty or honor

00:16:46.800 --> 00:16:48.160 line:80%
rule as emperor?

00:16:50.640 --> 00:16:52.000 line:80%
If he ever takes the throne,

00:16:52.760 --> 00:16:54.160 line:80%
he will be no wise ruler.

00:16:57.400 --> 00:16:58.360 line:80%
Grandfather,

00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:01.040 line:80%
you truly were wrong.

00:17:48.600 --> 00:17:49.960 line:80%
So you are not dead yet.

00:17:55.880 --> 00:17:56.960 line:80%
Kill me.

00:17:58.600 --> 00:18:00.200 line:80%
Take your revenge.

00:18:03.920 --> 00:18:05.240 line:80%
Fine.

00:18:09.840 --> 00:18:11.000 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing.

00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:14.680 line:80%
Before you die…

00:18:18.120 --> 00:18:19.400 line:80%
I want to ask you something.

00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:26.280 line:80%
Did you ever feel
the slightest love for me?

00:18:35.480 --> 00:18:37.320 line:80%
In my life,

00:18:38.200 --> 00:18:39.720 line:80%
I have deceived countless people.

00:18:42.280 --> 00:18:43.680 line:80%
Now that I am close to dying…

00:18:45.920 --> 00:18:47.120 line:80%
I suppose

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:49.720 line:80%
I should spin some comforting lies

00:18:51.600 --> 00:18:53.080 line:80%
so you would risk your life for me.

00:18:55.080 --> 00:18:57.360 line:80%
But strangely enough…

00:19:00.760 --> 00:19:03.280 line:80%
right now, I do not want to lie to you.

00:19:07.800 --> 00:19:09.040 line:80%
Not even a little.

00:19:11.120 --> 00:19:13.520 line:80%
I never felt the slightest love for you.

00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:24.920 line:80%
With the kind of man you are,

00:19:26.800 --> 00:19:28.280 line:80%
that is probably for the best.

00:19:36.360 --> 00:19:37.680 line:80%
Without you around…

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:42.280 line:80%
my days ahead…

00:19:45.240 --> 00:19:47.200 line:80%
will be freer than ever.

00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:04.000 line:80%
If you manage to survive,

00:20:04.760 --> 00:20:05.600 line:80%
take this

00:20:07.320 --> 00:20:09.160 line:80%
and go find Fan Changyu.

00:20:14.160 --> 00:20:15.000 line:80%
What is it?

00:20:19.240 --> 00:20:21.200 line:80%
You were with me once.

00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:23.920 line:80%
So I will leave you a way to survive.

00:20:25.400 --> 00:20:28.680 line:80%
Qi Min wants the whole world to suffer.

00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:30.880 line:80%
I, Sui Yuanqing,

00:20:32.080 --> 00:20:34.480 line:80%
only want him to suffer alone.

00:20:36.080 --> 00:20:37.880 line:80%
Why would she believe me?

00:21:02.400 --> 00:21:04.440 line:80%
This is the proper token from me…

00:21:08.280 --> 00:21:10.120 line:80%
to prove your loyalty.

00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:42.120 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing!

00:21:51.480 --> 00:21:53.680 line:20%
THREE DAYS LATER

00:21:53.760 --> 00:21:56.600 line:20%
Your Majesty,
I have a memorial to present.

00:21:56.680 --> 00:21:59.880 line:80%
Chancellor Wei's lax discipline
has bred near defiance.

00:21:59.960 --> 00:22:02.000 line:80%
Such an offense
should be punished severely.

00:22:07.760 --> 00:22:10.400 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li understands my mind.
Speak freely.

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:11.840 line:80%
Your Majesty,

00:22:11.920 --> 00:22:15.240 line:80%
Marquis Wu'an is Chancellor Wei's nephew,
brought up under his wing.

00:22:15.320 --> 00:22:16.240 line:80%
He dared cut off the ear

00:22:16.320 --> 00:22:19.600 line:80%
of the imperial envoy, Eunuch Li,
before the assembled army.

00:22:20.120 --> 00:22:22.720 line:80%
Such arrogance and tyranny
is nothing short of treason.

00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:26.720 line:80%
By the law, he should be executed
to serve as a warning to others.

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:32.200 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li speaks frankly.

00:22:34.040 --> 00:22:35.760 line:80%
Chancellor Wei, what say you?

00:22:36.680 --> 00:22:38.200 line:80%
In my view,

00:22:39.040 --> 00:22:40.360 line:80%
Eunuch Li kept insisting

00:22:40.440 --> 00:22:44.200 line:80%
that Marquis Wu'an intended to rebel.

00:22:44.280 --> 00:22:46.080 line:80%
So I believe

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:49.560 line:80%
the marquis simply acted
in anger and lost control.

00:22:51.120 --> 00:22:55.080 line:80%
After all, not everyone in this world
can be as gentle and composed

00:22:55.160 --> 00:22:57.800 line:80%
as Grand Tutor Li's grandson,
Military Administrator Li Huai'an.

00:22:57.880 --> 00:23:00.600 line:80%
Even when Your Majesty
suddenly changed your decision

00:23:00.680 --> 00:23:03.160 line:80%
and betrothed the Grand Princess
to another man,

00:23:03.240 --> 00:23:05.920 line:80%
he accepted it with admirable composure.

00:23:11.240 --> 00:23:13.840 line:80%
Chancellor Wei makes a fair point.

00:23:14.840 --> 00:23:16.560 line:80%
Military men

00:23:16.640 --> 00:23:18.720 line:80%
do tend to act a little roughly.

00:23:24.920 --> 00:23:25.840 line:80%
Chancellor Wei,

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:30.720 line:80%
half of He Jingyuan's command has fallen
into the hands of a mere village woman.

00:23:31.320 --> 00:23:34.640 line:80%
Captain Fan Changyu cannot even read
military maps or strategy manuals.

00:23:35.240 --> 00:23:37.200 line:80%
Yet through your private maneuvering,

00:23:37.280 --> 00:23:39.000 line:80%
she is now
a supervising commander of Jizhou.

00:23:39.080 --> 00:23:41.480 line:80%
The command office
is now in utter disarray.

00:23:41.560 --> 00:23:43.720 line:80%
May I ask, where is the army's discipline?

00:23:43.800 --> 00:23:45.640 line:80%
Where is the law of the realm?

00:23:45.720 --> 00:23:47.240 line:80%
Such a thing has truly happened?

00:23:50.560 --> 00:23:51.400 line:80%
Your Majesty,

00:23:51.480 --> 00:23:55.320 line:80%
both Marquis Wu'an and Captain Fan
have rendered great service.

00:23:55.400 --> 00:23:58.120 line:80%
Merit and fault must be judged separately.

00:23:58.200 --> 00:24:00.560 line:80%
What does Your Majesty think?

00:24:03.320 --> 00:24:04.800 line:80%
Report!

00:24:06.160 --> 00:24:07.080 line:80%
Your Majesty!

00:24:07.160 --> 00:24:09.480 line:80%
An 800-li express dispatch
has arrived from Jizhou.

00:24:09.560 --> 00:24:10.400 line:80%
-Bring it.
-Yes.

00:24:19.840 --> 00:24:21.120 line:80%
Excellent.

00:24:21.760 --> 00:24:23.800 line:80%
Marquis Wu'an joined forces
with Captain Fan

00:24:24.320 --> 00:24:25.760 line:80%
and has slain the rebel Sui Yuanhuai.

00:24:26.760 --> 00:24:29.600 line:80%
Prince Changxin and his two sons are dead.

00:24:29.680 --> 00:24:33.080 line:80%
The Sui line is extinguished.
The Chongzhou rebel army is no more.

00:24:33.160 --> 00:24:34.240 line:80%
Excellent!

00:24:39.880 --> 00:24:43.840 line:80%
A general and his commander working
in harmony to defeat the enemy leader.

00:24:44.520 --> 00:24:46.840 line:80%
This is a great fortune for me

00:24:46.920 --> 00:24:49.040 line:80%
and a blessing for Dayin.

00:24:52.680 --> 00:24:57.040 line:80%
The world is like a chessboard.
Every move brings a new game.

00:24:57.680 --> 00:25:00.760 line:80%
Since Marquis Wu'an and Captain Fan
have won such remarkable victories,

00:25:01.360 --> 00:25:04.600 line:80%
then I shall reward them.
And I shall reward them generously.

00:25:05.280 --> 00:25:07.000 line:80%
Your Majesty is wise.

00:25:09.800 --> 00:25:11.040 line:80%
Your Majesty is wise.

00:25:12.960 --> 00:25:16.040 line:80%
JIZHOU YAMEN

00:25:16.120 --> 00:25:19.120 line:80%
PEACE AND PROSPERITY ALONG THE BORDERS

00:25:28.320 --> 00:25:29.320 line:80%
My lord,

00:25:29.400 --> 00:25:31.160 line:80%
the Grand Princess leaves
for the capital tomorrow.

00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:33.480 line:80%
Captain Fan has arranged
a farewell banquet.

00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:35.680 line:80%
Will you attend?

00:25:53.120 --> 00:25:53.960 line:80%
Also,

00:25:54.040 --> 00:25:56.920 line:80%
at dawn, Marquis Wu'an's men
will escort the Grand Princess.

00:26:12.520 --> 00:26:13.960 line:80%
I am too ashamed to face them.

00:26:27.400 --> 00:26:28.520 line:80%
-Come on!
-Come on!

00:26:28.600 --> 00:26:30.480 line:80%
Pour it up!

00:26:31.000 --> 00:26:32.120 line:80%
HALL OF LETTERS

00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:51.080 line:80%
-Thirty-two!
-Twenty-two!

00:26:51.160 --> 00:26:52.400 line:80%
Cheers.

00:26:53.440 --> 00:26:54.840 line:80%
Drink up.

00:26:59.120 --> 00:27:01.560 line:80%
Everyone's already drunk
out of their minds.

00:27:01.640 --> 00:27:03.560 line:80%
Where is Military Administrator Li?

00:27:04.560 --> 00:27:06.360 line:80%
He caught a chill.

00:27:06.440 --> 00:27:07.720 line:80%
He will not make it tonight.

00:27:10.400 --> 00:27:11.320 line:80%
Everyone,

00:27:12.320 --> 00:27:15.240 line:80%
I cannot hold my drink.
After this cup, I will take my leave.

00:27:30.360 --> 00:27:32.000 line:80%
Safe travels, Your Highness.

00:27:42.720 --> 00:27:43.640 line:80%
Sit.

00:27:48.800 --> 00:27:50.280 line:80%
Her Highness returns
to the capital tomorrow.

00:27:51.200 --> 00:27:53.400 line:80%
If anyone has something to say,

00:27:53.480 --> 00:27:55.240 line:80%
tonight is the night.

00:27:57.040 --> 00:27:58.680 line:80%
-I will go!
-Sit down.

00:27:58.760 --> 00:27:59.600 line:80%
All right.

00:28:03.320 --> 00:28:04.360 line:80%
Go on then.

00:28:06.640 --> 00:28:07.760 line:80%
Where is he going?

00:28:09.200 --> 00:28:10.800 line:80%
Is he actually… He really went?

00:28:12.200 --> 00:28:14.320 line:80%
Your Highness! Your Highness, please wait.

00:28:15.560 --> 00:28:17.560 line:80%
-Your Highness.
-Her Highness does not wish to see you.

00:28:17.640 --> 00:28:19.360 line:80%
-I only wish to ask a few questions.
-Move aside.

00:28:21.120 --> 00:28:23.720 line:80%
I doubt Your Highness would return
with doubts left unresolved.

00:28:31.040 --> 00:28:32.080 line:80%
Leave us, Jianjia.

00:28:39.760 --> 00:28:40.600 line:80%
Allow me.

00:28:47.520 --> 00:28:48.400 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:28:49.760 --> 00:28:53.000 line:80%
Why have you suddenly decided
to return to the capital?

00:28:54.560 --> 00:28:56.640 line:80%
I have spent more than five months
in the northwest.

00:28:57.640 --> 00:28:59.200 line:80%
I am weary in both body and mind.

00:29:00.480 --> 00:29:01.840 line:80%
I've come to my senses.

00:29:03.200 --> 00:29:04.880 line:80%
I won't cling to what's futile.

00:29:07.400 --> 00:29:10.160 line:80%
Surely you must feel
greatly relieved, Headmaster.

00:29:13.040 --> 00:29:14.600 line:80%
Since you have reached such clarity,

00:29:15.440 --> 00:29:17.280 line:80%
I ought to offer my congratulations.

00:29:18.240 --> 00:29:19.320 line:80%
But there are words

00:29:20.720 --> 00:29:23.560 line:80%
I have kept in my heart for a long time.
I have long wished to share them.

00:29:25.000 --> 00:29:26.440 line:80%
Yet the rules of my clan are strict.

00:29:26.520 --> 00:29:27.440 line:80%
I dared not overstep.

00:29:30.320 --> 00:29:31.640 line:80%
So a few days ago,

00:29:32.880 --> 00:29:34.160 line:80%
I returned to Hejian

00:29:35.840 --> 00:29:37.520 line:80%
and knelt in the ancestral hall
for three days.

00:29:39.520 --> 00:29:41.360 line:80%
Only after receiving
the clan elder's pardon

00:29:42.680 --> 00:29:43.800 line:80%
did I dare come here

00:29:45.000 --> 00:29:46.640 line:80%
to speak my heart before Your Highness.

00:29:50.040 --> 00:29:51.080 line:80%
Go on.

00:29:53.960 --> 00:29:54.800 line:80%
Changyu.

00:29:57.160 --> 00:29:58.280 line:80%
-I…
-Easy there.

00:29:58.360 --> 00:30:00.560 line:80%
I need to drink a few cups with you alone.

00:30:01.280 --> 00:30:02.920 line:80%
Do you still have wine?

00:30:04.640 --> 00:30:06.920 line:80%
Let me… Let me speak honestly.

00:30:08.120 --> 00:30:11.680 line:80%
I, Jin Yuanbao, have never
respected anyone, but I respect you.

00:30:12.640 --> 00:30:14.520 line:80%
Before I met you,

00:30:14.600 --> 00:30:16.400 line:80%
I never believed

00:30:16.480 --> 00:30:19.560 line:80%
a woman with such thin arms and legs

00:30:19.640 --> 00:30:21.360 line:80%
could fight on a battlefield.

00:30:22.080 --> 00:30:25.120 line:80%
-With a build like yours?
-Never heard of it.

00:30:25.200 --> 00:30:26.040 line:80%
But Changyu can.

00:30:26.120 --> 00:30:28.360 line:80%
That is why I respect you.

00:30:28.440 --> 00:30:31.120 line:80%
-All of us respect you.
-Come on.

00:30:36.040 --> 00:30:36.920 line:80%
Come.

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:39.920 line:80%
Let's all toast to Captain Fan. Come on.

00:30:40.000 --> 00:30:41.200 line:80%
-Come.
-Folks.

00:30:41.280 --> 00:30:42.560 line:80%
-Pour the wine.
-Fill the cups!

00:30:43.240 --> 00:30:45.480 line:80%
My wife cannot hold her drink.
I will drink for her.

00:30:47.720 --> 00:30:49.280 line:80%
Wife? What wife?

00:30:49.960 --> 00:30:52.120 line:80%
She is the head of your household.

00:30:52.840 --> 00:30:54.680 line:80%
Everyone in Lin'an knows that.

00:30:54.760 --> 00:30:56.640 line:80%
You are the Fan family's
live-in son-in-law.

00:30:56.720 --> 00:30:59.680 line:80%
Once you marry in, you listen
to the head of the house. Right?

00:30:59.760 --> 00:31:00.600 line:80%
That is right.

00:31:00.680 --> 00:31:03.280 line:80%
You walk around these days all dignified.

00:31:03.360 --> 00:31:06.120 line:80%
Yes, yes, Marquis Wu'an.

00:31:06.200 --> 00:31:09.160 line:80%
But you bowed at the wedding altar.
You cannot deny that.

00:31:09.240 --> 00:31:10.560 line:80%
You cannot deny it.

00:31:12.720 --> 00:31:16.000 line:80%
What nonsense about live-in husbands?
I can drink this myself.

00:31:29.920 --> 00:31:32.000 line:80%
I'm getting old.
I can't recall what we were saying.

00:31:32.080 --> 00:31:34.240 line:80%
Not much of a drinker.
I could barely hold my cup steady.

00:31:35.200 --> 00:31:37.000 line:80%
My wife and I will take our leave.

00:31:37.080 --> 00:31:39.800 line:80%
-Everyone keep drinking.
-Changyu.

00:31:39.880 --> 00:31:40.800 line:80%
Well…

00:31:42.560 --> 00:31:43.400 line:80%
A hundred years ago,

00:31:43.480 --> 00:31:44.440 line:80%
CALMING WAVES PAVILION

00:31:44.520 --> 00:31:47.080 line:80%
the Gongsun clan stood
at the height of its glory.

00:31:48.600 --> 00:31:51.240 line:80%
For generations, the empresses
came from our family.

00:31:53.080 --> 00:31:54.520 line:80%
But great height draws danger.

00:31:55.280 --> 00:31:56.720 line:80%
Our fall was a tragic one.

00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:58.960 line:80%
During the reign of the founding emperor,

00:32:00.000 --> 00:32:01.880 line:80%
a dragon robe was found
inside the Eastern Palace.

00:32:04.200 --> 00:32:06.720 line:80%
Crown Prince Shaoyang was reduced
to a commoner.

00:32:08.360 --> 00:32:10.040 line:80%
Two empresses of the Gongsun family

00:32:10.920 --> 00:32:12.360 line:80%
hanged themselves in the palace.

00:32:12.440 --> 00:32:13.800 line:80%
The entire Gongsun clan

00:32:14.840 --> 00:32:16.600 line:80%
was confiscated and exiled.

00:32:18.720 --> 00:32:21.560 line:80%
Even the plaque above the Imperial Library
at Luyuan Academy

00:32:21.640 --> 00:32:23.240 line:80%
was nearly taken down.

00:32:24.920 --> 00:32:26.120 line:80%
I know of that case.

00:32:27.160 --> 00:32:28.360 line:80%
It was determined later

00:32:29.120 --> 00:32:30.440 line:80%
that the Gongsun case

00:32:31.720 --> 00:32:34.000 line:80%
was a wrongful accusation,
a frame-up by a prince.

00:32:37.080 --> 00:32:40.240 line:80%
In this world, there is no such thing
as a flawless frame-up.

00:32:41.240 --> 00:32:43.880 line:80%
In truth, the emperor on the throne
simply could no longer

00:32:43.960 --> 00:32:45.840 line:80%
tolerate the Gongsun clan.

00:32:47.400 --> 00:32:48.520 line:80%
A surviving branch of our clan

00:32:49.280 --> 00:32:51.520 line:80%
has lingered on at Luyuan Academy
for a hundred years.

00:32:53.960 --> 00:32:56.320 line:80%
The first rule in our clan law was this.

00:32:57.200 --> 00:32:58.200 line:80%
No Gongsun may enter official service.

00:33:03.040 --> 00:33:04.040 line:80%
The truth is,

00:33:05.640 --> 00:33:07.760 line:80%
the day Your Highness arrived
at Luyuan Academy,

00:33:08.840 --> 00:33:10.560 line:80%
I already knew you were a woman.

00:33:12.160 --> 00:33:14.880 line:80%
When we first played the Go chess game
at the Imperial Library,

00:33:15.400 --> 00:33:16.880 line:80%
I realized something else.

00:33:18.480 --> 00:33:21.440 line:80%
The one who broke my position
in the Rain Pavilion was you.

00:33:23.760 --> 00:33:24.640 line:80%
But when I learned

00:33:26.920 --> 00:33:29.040 line:80%
that the woman I had admired for so long

00:33:30.680 --> 00:33:32.160 line:80%
was the Grand Princess,

00:33:33.800 --> 00:33:35.480 line:80%
I felt no joy.

00:33:38.000 --> 00:33:39.400 line:80%
Only the feeling that fate was mocking me.

00:33:41.480 --> 00:33:43.680 line:80%
Then why tell me

00:33:45.600 --> 00:33:46.800 line:80%
all of this now?

00:33:57.520 --> 00:33:59.240 line:80%
I wish to ask for Your Highness's hand.

00:34:02.160 --> 00:34:03.000 line:80%
I have

00:34:05.400 --> 00:34:06.640 line:80%
admired you for a long time.

00:34:07.400 --> 00:34:09.880 line:80%
Tonight, I dare ask Your Highness this.

00:34:11.080 --> 00:34:12.160 line:80%
If one day

00:34:13.160 --> 00:34:14.320 line:80%
I help Jiuheng

00:34:14.959 --> 00:34:16.680 line:80%
bring down Wei Yan and the Li clan,

00:34:18.840 --> 00:34:19.920 line:80%
is Your Highness

00:34:20.999 --> 00:34:22.880 line:80%
willing to live with me in Hejian,

00:34:22.959 --> 00:34:24.640 line:80%
free from the cares of the world?

00:34:31.479 --> 00:34:32.880 line:80%
Your Highness need not worry.

00:34:33.680 --> 00:34:35.959 line:80%
My family has means.
We would live comfortably.

00:34:36.039 --> 00:34:37.200 line:80%
Your Highness would not suffer.

00:34:37.920 --> 00:34:40.999 line:80%
-Though Hejian may not compare to--
-And if I say no?

00:34:54.959 --> 00:34:55.920 line:80%
Then…

00:35:00.360 --> 00:35:01.600 line:80%
I have spoken out of turn.

00:35:03.120 --> 00:35:04.440 line:80%
Please forgive my presumption.

00:35:19.040 --> 00:35:20.360 line:80%
You blockhead.

00:35:23.200 --> 00:35:24.200 line:80%
I will take

00:35:25.120 --> 00:35:27.680 line:80%
the 10,000 volumes
in your family's library

00:35:28.400 --> 00:35:29.440 line:80%
as my bride price.

00:35:30.440 --> 00:35:31.360 line:80%
Do you agree?

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:38.520 line:80%
Are you hesitating?

00:35:43.640 --> 00:35:46.000 line:80%
Yes. Yes, I agree. I agree to everything.

00:35:47.320 --> 00:35:50.120 line:80%
The Gongsun family has 12 library halls.

00:35:51.160 --> 00:35:52.320 line:80%
May I ask, Your Highness,

00:35:52.960 --> 00:35:54.200 line:80%
which one you want?

00:35:54.280 --> 00:35:55.760 line:80%
All of them.

00:35:58.280 --> 00:35:59.280 line:80%
Good.

00:36:01.040 --> 00:36:01.880 line:80%
Very good.

00:36:07.960 --> 00:36:10.080 line:80%
Let go of me.

00:36:14.520 --> 00:36:16.400 line:80%
Where are you taking me?

00:36:17.480 --> 00:36:19.560 line:80%
You've had too much to drink.
Let's get you to bed.

00:36:20.160 --> 00:36:22.120 line:80%
I am not drunk, Marquis.

00:36:28.240 --> 00:36:29.920 line:80%
That word again. Marquis.

00:36:31.480 --> 00:36:33.040 line:80%
Can you stop calling me that?

00:36:36.240 --> 00:36:37.600 line:80%
Call me anything,

00:36:38.600 --> 00:36:40.000 line:80%
except that.

00:37:00.600 --> 00:37:02.040 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:37:03.280 --> 00:37:04.600 line:80%
Your name is Yan Zheng.

00:37:10.920 --> 00:37:11.920 line:80%
<i>From now on,</i>

00:37:13.040 --> 00:37:15.320 line:80%
can I call you Yan Zheng?

00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:30.000 line:80%
Your hand…

00:37:31.840 --> 00:37:32.840 line:80%
Does it hurt?

00:37:53.000 --> 00:37:53.840 line:80%
Changyu.

00:37:57.360 --> 00:37:58.320 line:80%
Kiss me.

00:38:59.360 --> 00:39:01.120 line:80%
If you miss me, write me a letter.

00:39:01.960 --> 00:39:03.200 line:80%
I may not understand it fully, but still.

00:39:08.360 --> 00:39:09.360 line:80%
I should be going.

00:39:10.000 --> 00:39:10.840 line:80%
Safe travels.

00:39:33.440 --> 00:39:34.280 line:80%
I am leaving.

00:40:00.880 --> 00:40:02.040 line:80%
If you hate to part so much,

00:40:02.560 --> 00:40:04.280 line:80%
why did you not see her off yourself?

00:40:04.360 --> 00:40:06.760 line:80%
If I had gone,
I might not have let her leave.

00:40:12.280 --> 00:40:14.920 line:80%
A promise is a promise.
Since I gave you my word, it stands.

00:40:16.120 --> 00:40:18.840 line:80%
Since when did it become my fault
for ruining your chances?

00:40:20.880 --> 00:40:22.160 line:80%
We have made an agreement.

00:40:22.680 --> 00:40:24.840 line:80%
Once everything is settled,
we will return to Hejian

00:40:25.520 --> 00:40:27.680 line:80%
and find a quiet place
to spend the rest of our lives.

00:40:27.760 --> 00:40:29.920 line:80%
But the storm in the capital

00:40:30.000 --> 00:40:31.320 line:80%
can no longer be ignored.

00:40:33.160 --> 00:40:34.880 line:80%
Then it is time to return to the capital

00:40:35.560 --> 00:40:36.680 line:80%
and finish

00:40:37.200 --> 00:40:38.320 line:80%
what must be done.

00:40:42.320 --> 00:40:48.080 line:20%
THE CAPITAL

00:40:54.800 --> 00:40:56.200 line:80%
Not bad, not bad.

00:40:59.400 --> 00:41:00.480 line:80%
Have another drink.

00:41:01.040 --> 00:41:02.120 line:80%
-I want that one.
-Here.

00:41:02.200 --> 00:41:03.480 line:80%
-Drink up.
-All right.

00:41:05.800 --> 00:41:08.160 line:80%
-Do not fuss.
-One more cup.

00:41:10.240 --> 00:41:11.080 line:80%
Mr. Li Huaiqin.

00:41:13.600 --> 00:41:16.680 line:80%
I was wondering why I had not seen Yueli
these past few days.

00:41:19.160 --> 00:41:22.040 line:80%
Turns out someone has been holed up
at Jingque House and refuses to leave.

00:41:28.680 --> 00:41:30.400 line:80%
Wei Xuan,

00:41:30.480 --> 00:41:32.800 line:80%
are you not supposed to be serving
in the northwest?

00:41:34.680 --> 00:41:36.240 line:80%
LI HUAIQIN, LI XING'S YOUNGEST GRANDSON

00:41:36.320 --> 00:41:38.680 line:80%
I heard Marquis Wu'an has returned.

00:41:39.920 --> 00:41:41.960 line:80%
What is this? Stepping aside
to make way for him?

00:41:51.080 --> 00:41:52.120 line:80%
Get out.

00:41:55.680 --> 00:41:58.960 line:80%
Seems the stray can never compare
to the real son of the house.

00:42:01.520 --> 00:42:03.400 line:80%
From the looks of it, Marquis Wu'an

00:42:03.480 --> 00:42:05.440 line:80%
must be Chancellor Wei's
true flesh and blood.

00:42:06.840 --> 00:42:07.800 line:80%
Everyone leave.

00:42:09.320 --> 00:42:10.200 line:80%
Yes.

00:42:24.640 --> 00:42:26.880 line:80%
Say that again.

00:42:27.840 --> 00:42:29.160 line:80%
Why play dumb?

00:42:29.240 --> 00:42:30.880 line:80%
The entire capital is talking about it.

00:42:31.400 --> 00:42:33.160 line:80%
They say the Chancellor
and his wife are at odds.

00:42:34.680 --> 00:42:36.720 line:80%
And that you are not even his son.

00:42:42.600 --> 00:42:43.720 line:80%
Wei Xuan, you dare?

00:42:46.640 --> 00:42:47.720 line:80%
You are just a bastard.

00:42:48.560 --> 00:42:51.320 line:80%
All day, you throw your weight around
on Chancellor Wei's name.

00:42:51.400 --> 00:42:53.120 line:80%
And your mother? She's nothing.

00:42:53.200 --> 00:42:56.520 line:80%
Everyone knows Chancellor Wei's true love
was Lady Qi from the palace.

00:42:59.160 --> 00:43:00.440 line:80%
Li Huaiqin,

00:43:00.960 --> 00:43:02.400 line:80%
you're spewing utter nonsense.

00:43:02.480 --> 00:43:05.520 line:80%
If this were the battlefield,
I would have taken your head already.

00:43:06.440 --> 00:43:07.880 line:80%
I will give you one chance.

00:43:07.960 --> 00:43:10.520 line:80%
Shout three times,
"Li is inferior to Wei,"

00:43:11.440 --> 00:43:13.200 line:80%
and I will spare you today.

00:43:13.280 --> 00:43:14.480 line:80%
Bah!

00:43:14.560 --> 00:43:16.360 line:80%
Who do you think you are, Wei Xuan?

00:43:16.440 --> 00:43:17.760 line:80%
Li inferior to Wei?

00:43:17.840 --> 00:43:19.000 line:80%
Wei is inferior to Xie!

00:43:22.720 --> 00:43:23.560 line:80%
Wei Xuan!

00:43:29.080 --> 00:43:31.480 line:80%
END CREDIT SCENE

00:44:10.120 --> 00:44:11.680 line:80%
Changyu and the Marquis…

00:44:11.760 --> 00:44:13.640 line:80%
-They… They…
-What is it?

00:44:14.160 --> 00:44:15.000 line:80%
Come look for yourself.

00:44:15.080 --> 00:44:16.160 line:80%
Look, look!

00:44:19.320 --> 00:44:21.000 line:80%
-The Marquis…
-What Marquis?

00:44:21.080 --> 00:44:22.720 line:80%
I was just about to curse him out.

00:44:23.240 --> 00:44:26.040 line:80%
One moment, he pretends to be
a meek Fan family live-in son-in-law.

00:44:26.120 --> 00:44:28.400 line:80%
Next moment, he is putting on airs
as Marquis Wu'an.

00:44:28.480 --> 00:44:30.960 line:80%
Now he'll marry the princess
and become imperial consort.

